text: "Written in the Stars" is a 1999 song by Elton John featuring LeAnn Rimes. It was featured in the 1999 musical Aida and LeAnn Rimes 2002 album I Need You. It went to number 10 in the United Kingdom, number 29 in the United States, number 22 in Canada, number 18 in Italy, number 20 in Iceland, number 14 in Scotland, number 28 in Austria and number 34 in Switzerland. ==Track listing== CD single # "Written in the Stars" – 4:17 # "Written in the Stars" (Alternate Version) – 4:24 # "Various Snippets" (My Strongest Suit/Not Me/A Step Too Far) – 2:27 ==References== Category:1999 songs Category:Elton John songs Category:LeAnn Rimes songs
title: Written in the Stars (Elton John and LeAnn Rimes song)
